+	 * Put the rq online, if not already. This happens:
+	 *
+	 * 1) In the early boot process, because we build the real domains
+	 *    after all cpus have been brought up.
+	 *
+	 * 2) At runtime, if cpuset_cpu_active() fails to rebuild the
+	 *    domains.
